# {{ project_name }}

This project was generated from a Copier template and provides a Pixi-managed Nextflow DSL2 starter workflow for bioinformatics analyses.

## What this scaffold includes

- Pixi environment and task management
- Nextflow DSL2 workflow entry point
- A generation-time execution target: **{{ 'Slurm' if has_slurm else 'local' }}**
